On to the Update:

How Apple Intelligence Works
----------------------------

From Android Authority ( https://www.androidauthority.com/apple-foundation-=
models-vs-chatgpt-3450620/ ) :

Apple announced a litany of AI features for iPhone, iPad, Mac, and Siri at =
WWDC 2024 yesterday, but in a surprising twist, didn=E2=80=99t elaborate on=
 the generative AI models it will use to power them. While rumors indicated=
 that the company would rely on OpenAI=E2=80=99s ChatGPT or Google=E2=80=99=
s Gemini, they turned out to be only half-true. For example, while a ChatGP=
T integration is indeed coming to iOS, iPadOS, and macOS later this year, i=
t won=E2=80=99t power the revamped Siri or other Apple Intelligence feature=
s.

But thanks to a new post on Apple=E2=80=99s machine learning research blog =
( https://machinelearning.apple.com/research/introducing-apple-foundation-m=
odels ) , we now know more about the company=E2=80=99s AI strategy for 2024=
 and beyond. For starters, the company will rely on its own large language =
models (LLMs) rather than licensing third-party offerings from the likes of=
 Google and OpenAI.

Apple says its foundation models have been =E2=80=9Cfine-tuned for user exp=
eriences such as writing and refining text, prioritizing and summarizing no=
tifications, creating playful images for conversations with family and frie=
nds, and taking in-app actions to simplify interactions across apps.=E2=80=
=9D The blog post then delves into some of the technical aspects behind its=
 generative AI models, with the main focus being on optimization for low la=
tency and on-device performance.

I linked to that Apple blog post in yesterday=E2=80=99s Update ( https://st=
ratechery.com/2024/wwdc-apple-intelligence-apple-aggregates-ai/?access_toke=
n=3DeyJhbGciOiJSUzI1NiIsImtpZCI6InN0cmF0ZWNoZXJ5LnBhc3Nwb3J0Lm9ubGluZSIsInR=
5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJhdWQiOiJzdHJhdGVjaGVyeS5wYXNzcG9ydC5vbmxpbmUiLCJhenAiOiJIS=
0xjUzREd1Nod1AyWURLYmZQV00xIiwiZW50Ijp7InVyaSI6WyJodHRwczovL3N0cmF0ZWNoZXJ5=
LmNvbS8yMDI0L3d3ZGMtYXBwbGUtaW50ZWxsaWdlbmNlLWFwcGxlLWFnZ3JlZ2F0ZXMtYWkvIl1=
9LCJleHAiOjE3MjA3Nzg4MjYsImlhdCI6MTcxODE4NjgyNiwiaXNzIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly9hcGkucG=
